{"tid":1056653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富士攝影拒絕為網上購物客戶提供保養","createTime":"2019-03-11T10:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:41:55.000Z","uid":389,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a2e24ffca454085267f9977d6ab4f48b030d5893","tid":1056653,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"攝台太多富士打手，而且呢單野上左好多page<br />\n<br />\n好出名既Fujifilm近日嚴格執行保養規則<br />\n單據必須蓋印先有保養<br />\n<br />\n但好多網民就屌晒富士老母<br />\n因為富士自己分銷商同埋自己e-shop既行貨都係係印既<br />\n<br />\n變相即係買e-shop行貨=水貨無保養<br />\n<br />\n食客戶夾棍<br />\n<br />\n大家買相機要小心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gb7M2gu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgb7M2gu.png&h=62455cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uogVa9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuogVa9Q.png&h=869616fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PawufBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPawufBw.png&h=89e22575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉自傑出公關"},{"pid":"85adee9f8a5db353e860fad1ca3b554f15040fd1","tid":1056653,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"唔明要保用證書同收據唔係正常"},{"pid":"324a4dd6c91dd01555b279f9edd815c3f189df57","tid":1056653,"uid":83344,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"正常行貨serial no. 已有晒record一check 就知行定水，唔明點解搞咁多野"},{"pid":"6c06a24d4e5eb527de94b00ff72a7d1df0020a09","tid":1056653,"uid":18948,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"屌同啲全球保養嘅嘢一尻樣，香港不是全球一部份"},{"pid":"4dfb1edc63f2a2c3cba8b8358151bffffb6cfdfb","tid":1056653,"uid":389,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"85adee9f8a5db353e860fad1ca3b554f15040fd1","tid":1056653,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"唔明要保用證書同收據唔係正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"佢自己鋪同埋e shop都無吸印<br />\n<br />\n無吸引既保用證=唔保養<br />\n<br />\n佢而家叫人去分銷既鋪頭吸引<br />\n富士唔會吸印<br />\n<br />\n即係唔保富士自己賣出去果啲行貨"},{"pid":"28505ce811e201b8b6a6fb053664c8bf8b0a0225","tid":1056653,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":75,"score":-74,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b161f909687e2e85603593aeb5e90216822e674f","tid":1056653,"uid":9793,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"28505ce811e201b8b6a6fb053664c8bf8b0a0225","tid":1056653,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":75,"score":-74,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"有單都無用 因為就算你係fujifilm既指定分銷商到買都唔一定有印仔。"},{"pid":"a102c6a26229bc349706aef829db0976421b0bdb","tid":1056653,"uid":33907,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"28505ce811e201b8b6a6fb053664c8bf8b0a0225","tid":1056653,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":75,"score":-74,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"你食屎啦 講緊e-shop買完唔吸啊 知唔撚知咩叫網上購物啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e7f7e51d01808e130dabd707e173200bbbf139","tid":1056653,"uid":51932,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"係佢eshop 買都可以尻答，好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37c889f785863395358ee55493d2095102072a7","tid":1056653,"uid":389,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"28505ce811e201b8b6a6fb053664c8bf8b0a0225","tid":1056653,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":75,"score":-74,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"以為走出公海少啲打手<br />\n點知多左文盲"},{"pid":"4ae332e3c32051ea50bb4895de054be79d5311fe","tid":1056653,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a102c6a26229bc349706aef82